      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA procedures documented and version-controlled CFD solver used throughout the study.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2021 R2 was used under a validated SQA framework. Solver version control, input file archiving, and audit trail documentation satisfy MRL 2 requirements for software quality assurance."
