      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verification against canonical benchmark cases with documented order-of-accuracy results.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver was verified against the lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmarks. Observed order of accuracy was consistent with the formal second-order scheme, confirming code correctness for the relevant flow regime."
