      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for primary QoI with GCI < 5% on fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed. GCI for the normalized index of hemolysis on the fine mesh was 2.8%, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Temporal discretization error was assessed via time-step halving with negligible change in QoI."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
