      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and boundary conditions in simulation match experimental conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity, temperature) were documented in the validation dataset. CFD boundary conditions were set to match experimental values; deviations were within published measurement uncertainty bands."
