      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation are the same as or directly related to the QoIs in the COU.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used in validation is directly mapped to the relative hemolysis index (RH) acceptance criterion in the COU. The power-law hemolysis model scalar is the primary QoI in both validation and prediction contexts."
    },
