    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model meets the requirements for MRL 2 at medium model influence and high decision consequence. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required levels. The remaining six factors were scoped out as not required at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
